      <title><![CDATA[The Book of Rites, Early Education and Gender Differentiation [Literary Excerpt]]]></title>
      <link>https://cyh.rrchnm.org/items/show/194</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<div class="element-set">
    <h2>Dublin Core</h2>
        <div id="dublin-core-title" class="element">
